OL,3,CPlaid Cymru calls for new Wales Bill
OL,4,Cto give it powers on par with Scotland
OL,6,FPlaid Cymru is calling for Wales to be
OL,7,Fgiven the same powers of control as
OL,8,FScotland.
OL,10,FTransport, crown estate, justice and
OL,11,Fpolicing, energy, taxation and welfare
OL,12,Fare among the powers held by Scotland
OL,13,Fbut currently unavailable to Wales.
OL,15,FPlaid Cymru leader Rhun ap Iorwerth
OL,16,Fand the party's Westminster leader Liz
OL,17,FSaville Roberts are set to ask for "a
OL,18,FWales Bill based on the premise of
OL,19,Fparity of powers with Scotland" when
OL,20,Fthey meet with Welsh Secretary Jo
OL,21,FStevens.
