OL,3,CPlaid Cymru calls for new Wales Bill
OL,4,Cto give it powers on par with Scotland
OL,6,FMr ap Iorwerth says "Wales deserves
OL,7,Fits fair share" and his party's call
OL,8,Ffor parity with Scotland is "about
OL,9,Fsecuring the powers needed to truly
OL,10,Fimprove the lives of people who live
OL,11,Fhere".
OL,13,FThe Plaid Cymru representatives will
OL,14,Falso press the case for scrapping the
OL,15,FBarnett Formula and introducing a
OL,16,Ffunding model which funds Wales
OL,17,Faccording to need, not population.
OL,19,FMr ap Iorwerth said: "Scotland has
OL,20,Fshown how these powers can be used to
OL,21,Fbetter serve the people.
