OL,3,CPlaid Cymru calls for new Wales Bill
OL,4,Cto give it powers on par with Scotland
OL,6,F"A devolved benefits system has
OL,7,Fshielded people in Scotland from some
OL,8,Fof the most brutal Westminster
OL,9,Fausterity, while the devolved Scottish
OL,10,FCrown Estate directly invests in
OL,11,Fdeprived coastal communities.
OL,13,F"If Scotland can do it, why not Wales?"
OL,15,FMs Saville Roberts said it was time to
OL,16,Fdeliver the biggest ever transfer of
OL,17,Fpowers out of Westminster, adding:
OL,18,F"Only with greater powers can we
OL,19,Fcreate a fairer future for our
OL,20,Fcommunities."
