OL,3,CPlaid Cymru calls for new Wales Bill
OL,4,Cto give it powers on par with Scotland
OL,6,FPlaid Cymru state that Scotland has
OL,7,Fauthority over rail infrastructure,
OL,8,Fwhereas Wales does not control its own
OL,9,Frailways or receive equivalent funding
OL,10,Ffor infrastructure.
OL,12,FManagement of the Crown Estate was
OL,13,Fdevolved to Scotland in 2017, which
OL,14,Fmeans that Scotland can maximise the
OL,15,Fpotential of its resources, and
OL,16,Frevenue is returned to Edinburgh
OL,17,Frather than Westminster, they add.
